  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\nHi, \r\nI recently used Openzepplin-contracts for my token sale contract, I found the code and documentation to be excellent thank you. \r\n\r\nAdditionally I wanted to be able to operate a private sale before going public so I created a contract that uses a simple disposable passphrase mechanism\r\n\r\nDoes this feature interest you? If so I'm happy to raise a PR. \r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\nPlease see [DisposableAccessCode](https://github.com/Metarei-network/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/DisposableAccessCode/contracts/security/DisposableAccessCode.sol)\r\n\r\nThank you\r\n\r\nTom",
